description: Perfectly situated on the corner of E Broadway and Farragut Road, this recently renovated 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo all on one level provides a variety of recreational amenities. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the walking/running trails, nearby marina, beachfront and water access, offering opportunities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Additionally, the property boasts stunning ocean views, providing a picturesque backdrop for everyday living. Watch the sunrise with coffee in hand on your easily accessible private porch. The open concept chef's stainless steel applianced kitchen has a large island with granite countertops and custom cabinetry making it fabulous for entertaining. The 2nd bedroom is the perfect work from home office, nursery, and/or guest room. AC, hardwood floors throughout, and private locked storage finish this rare opportunity.  Don't renew that lease before coming to see this Southie stunner!
